```ts
const quoteStep = (customer, quoteIndex, items) => {
  const billables = billingItems(items);
  const policyBase = sumBy(billables, basePremiumForItem);
  const surcharges = sumBy(billables, (item) => basePremiumForItem(item) * itemSurchargeRate(item));
  const discount = policyBase * policyDiscountRate(customer, quoteIndex);
  return { premium: Math.ceil(policyBase - discount + surcharges + PROCESSING_FEE) };
};
```

Bindings: `customer, quoteIndex, items, billables, policyBase, surcharges, discount, item` = 8 (mass 8)

Body refs/invocations:
- `billingItems(items)`: 3
- `sumBy(billables, basePremiumForItem)`: 4
